{"ts":"2026-06-26T06:21:23.116Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Designing the AI Control Center**\n\nI'm thrilled with the progress so far! Pages one and two, Blueprint and the Marketplace, compiled seamlessly in under five seconds. My focus has shifted to Page 3, specifically the Unified AI Control Center. Now, I'm diving into the design phase of this control center.\n\n\n**Inspecting the Control Center**\n\nI'm now deep in the `/app/platforms/control-center/page.tsx` file, looking closely at the interactive cockpit console. There are three tabs: 'fleet', 'gov', and 'spend'. I'm currently reviewing the 'fleet' tab's components, specifically lines 102 to 210, to understand its structure.\n\n\n**Analyzing Fleet Agent Display**\n\nI'm now zeroing in on the 'fleet' tab's implementation, focusing on the agent display within the cockpit. Specifically, I'm examining how agent instances are rendered, their statuses, and how interactions with the buttons dynamically update the active agent ID. I'm taking notes on how this structure can be optimized for larger fleets.\n\n\n**Examining Agent Performance Metrics**\n\nI'm now closely examining the display of specific performance metrics for the selected agent, particularly latency and active governance scan status, to ensure they're accurately and clearly displayed. The UI structure is solid, but I'm thinking about how to visualize these metrics for quick, at-a-glance assessments.\n\n\n**Visualizing Telemetry Waves**\n\nI'm now completely focused on integrating real-time SVG telemetry waves into the \"Fleet Telemetry\" panel. I envision each node displaying a unique, custom-designed SVG path reflecting its latency profile. The `tax` node will have a jittery wave, `telemetry` a smooth, fast one, and `sla-coord` a slow, heavy wave. I've designed sample paths for each; for example, `tax` might be: `d=\"M0 25 L20 22 L40 28 L60 10 L80 40 L100 20 L120 30 L140 5 L160 35 L180 25 L200 25\"` with `stroke=\"#E4000F\"`. I'm going for glowing lines.\n\n\n"}}
